                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6434" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0258</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8143 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百尺竿头更进一步：B企业费用管理流程优化之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">One Hundred Thousand Years Ahead: The Way to  Optimize the Expense Management Process of Enterprise B</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹翠珍，马雨欣，姬玉涵，贾雅婷，姚昱杉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">B房地产企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">费用管理；业务流程优化；DMAIC模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cost management; Business process optimization;DMAIC model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">房地产作为我国国民经济的支柱性产业，是推动我国经济发展的重要动力之一。B企业作为其中的佼佼者，为了顺应数字经济时代的发展，建立了财务共享服务中心。但是随着公司规模的不断扩大，部分费用管理流程不能满足企业精细化管理的需要，财务共享中心的刘总经理为了解决这个问题，进一步降低企业管理成本，实时掌握财务信息和业务信息，科学快速地进行管理决策，决定对费用管理流程进行优化。那么，如何判断哪些费用管理流程存在问题？又如何对其进行优化？这引起了刘总及其他高层管理人员的思考。本案例旨在通过对B企业费用管理流程的优化，实现费用精细化管理的目标，加深学员对六西格玛管理理论和DMAIC模型的学习，使学员掌握费用管理流程优化的相关知识，启发其对大型企业集团财务共享服务中心流程如何优化的深入思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a pillar industry of our country&#39;s national economy, real estate is one of the important driving forces for our country&#39;s economic development. B company has established a Financial Shared Service Center as a leader among them in order to adapt to the development of the digital economy era. However, as the company continues to expand, part of the expense management process cannot meet the needs of enterprise refined management. In order to overcome this problem, General Manager Liu of the Financial Shared Service Center further reduces enterprise management costs, grasps financial information and business information in real time, so as to scientifically make management decisions quickly and decide to optimize the expense management process. So, how to judge which expense management process has problems? How to optimize it? This aroused the thinking of Mr. Liu and other senior managers. This case aims to achieve the goal of refined cost management by optimizing the cost management process of B company deepen the students&#39; learning of Six Sigma management theory and DMAIC model, so that the students can master the relevant knowledge of cost management process optimization, and inspire them to large enterprises. In-depth consideration how to optimize the process of the group Financial Shared Service Center.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《企业管理》、《六西格玛管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务流程管理；流程优选矩阵FTE法；六西格玛管理理论；DMAIC模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-08</td>
                            </tr>
